**Architecture:** Keep the current `visualViewport.resize` keyboard-follow flow intact and make a single guarded change at the existing auto-`blur()` branch in the home chat view. Reuse the existing `bjsdk.isIOS` platform signal so only iOS skips viewport-driven auto blur; all explicit blur paths and Android logic remain unchanged.

**Tech Stack:** Vue 3 single-file component, Vue CLI 4, beta-jsdk, ESLint

